Cliffjumper pulled the trigger, and the laser roared out, but missed the
target when Cliffjumper's aim was thrown off by a large stone that hit
him in the head. The inorganic missile smashed off Cliffjumper's head,
as he turned his gun. When he turned his head to see where the rock had
came from, a large purple hand swatted him in the flace, sending a
screaming Autobot sailing. 

"What it halfpint." is what Cliffjumper heard, as he looked up to see a
badly dammaged, transformed, and angry Slugslinger stood above him,
fists clenched. Cliffjumper aimed his gun at the Decepticon, but
Caliburst was quicker to react, as he grabbed his gun, and blasted
Cliffjumper in the side, then did a kick up, and leapt largely into a
back flip, transforming into Calibursts sub machine gun. Cliffjumper
opened his eyes again after the pain subsided, and saw the barrel of
Caliburst. "Rust in Pieces Autobot." SLugslinger said with disdain.
